Interface KerberosConfigDataFile

  • All Superinterfaces:
    KerberosDataFile
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    KerberosConfigDataFileReader, KerberosConfigDataFileWriter

    public interface KerberosConfigDataFile
extends KerberosDataFile
    KerberosConfigDataFile declares the default data file name and the common record column names for the Kerberos configuration data files.
